  "text": "Bootstrap support (BS) values from the MP and ML analyses as well as posterior probabilities (PP) from the BI analysis were mapped onto the BI 50% majority rule consensus tree with SUMTREES version 3.3.1, which is part of the DENDROPY 3.8.0 package [CITATION_1] . BS values ≥ 70 and PP values ≥ 0.95 were interpreted as positive support.",
